          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "<strong>What fuel types are FUELAB products compatible with?</strong>",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_svg": "",
            "header_image_width": 25,
            "faq_answer": "<p>Many FUELAB fuel system components are designed to support a variety of fuel types, including gasoline, ethanol blends, methanol, and diesel, depending on the product. Always check the product specifications to ensure compatibility with your application.</p>",
