          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "<strong>Can I build a complete fuel system with FUELAB components?</strong>",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_svg": "",
            "header_image_width": 25,
            "faq_answer": "<p>Yes. FUELAB offers fuel pumps, pressure regulators, filters, surge tanks, controllers, fittings, and accessories that work together as a complete fuel delivery solution for a wide range of performance applications.</p>",
